originalText.text: Horrible tailoring! They don’t know how to do their jobs at all! And the owner has a very horrible attitude toward customer!! Why in business if you care so little about your customer? They totally ruined my sweater and skirt: used a different color and different type of thread to fix my sweater; and did the skirt inside out!? AND the owner told me that it was me who ruined them?! I send the clothes in for loose weaving and threading! Don’t do anything if you don’t know how to do tailoring! At least feel sorry about adding more damage to them!! Jeez!!! DO NOT ever come here if you don’t want to ruin your clothes!

originalText.text: All of the services I’ve had them provide in the past turned out great. My family has been using Green City for years for repairs, alterations and their laundry delivery service. The only time we had an item returned to us damaged was a delicate that we accidentally put in the wash-and-fold service bag for delivery. Even though it was our fault, the manager was very kind and understanding. They repaired the damage and delivered it back to us, free of charge. Highly recommend and look forward to coming back!

originalText.text:
Green City Cleaners is the only laundry service I’ve used in the past two years. The manager, Billy, is very kind and always helpful. They have helped me with repairs, alterations, and basic cleaning services.
The express, same-day delivery service is convenient and easy to schedule. The pricing for all of the services are very affordable, especially for the neighborhood.

originalText.text:
DO NOT GO THERE!!! THEY ARE UNPROFESSIONAL AND BULLIES!!!
We’ve been sending out laundry bags with our smaller sorting bags with socks, delicates, etc. They promised that they’ll separate laundry from different households but we found an unidentified sock in our zipped sorting bag.

When we asked for explanation on how sth from another household got into our zipped sorting bag, the male manager was defensive & disrespectful and told us it can happen at any stage of your cleaning / drying  processes and since we got an extra sock - as sth we should be grateful for(?!!!!) - he couldn’t give us refund. He was even dangling the sock in front of the eyes of my bf and that was OUTRAGEOUS !!!!

I will recommend anyone in the neighborhood to AVOID this cleaner not only for they BAD CLEANING PRACTICES but also RIDICULOUS ATTITUDES!
